<HEADLINE> Pakistan's Trade Deficit Drops </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, January 8 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan's trade deficit
dropped by 36 percent to 1.116 billion U.S. dollars during the
