out a package of comprehensive measures to deal with the issue of
prison overcrowding and the situation would be improved gradually.
</P>
<P>
The CSD administers a wide range of services for adult and
young offenders, drug addicts and offenders with psychiatric
problems.
</P>
<P>
Before attending the department's annual parade, Tung visited
Hong Kong's top-security prison of Stanley.
</P>
<P>
Accompanied by Raymond Lai Ming-kee, commissioner of the CSD,
Tung visited several workshops, the kitchen, a prison
accommodation hall and the prison hospital. He was also briefed
about the prison's management and operation.  
</P>
