of friendship between the two countries and that Morocco wishes to
strengthen its ties with China.
</P>
<P>
The king congratulated China on the resumption of exercise of
sovereignty over Hong Kong and viewed it as "a historic event of
great importance" and "a happy event."
</P>
<P>
