Jason Stoltenberg, who beat another Frenchman Nicolas Escude, 6-7
(3-7), 6-1, 7-5.
</P>
<P>
Agassi's semi-final opponent is Australia's Lleyton Hewitt, who
ousted American Vince Spadea, 7-5, 3-6, 6-1, who is the third
Australian semifinalist. 
