The airline based in this capital of Zhejiang Province rented
two A320 planes in September.
</P>
<P>
Since its establishment in 1987, Zhejiang Airlines has formed
an air transport network linking the provincial capital with major
Chinese cities.
</P>
<P>
Since A320 aircraft entered the Chinese market in 1995, 17
planes have gone into operation.  
